# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Local caches of SOURCE documents — never commit these.
# Source documents are LINKED, not redistributed (see docs/METHODOLOGY.md).
# The extracted quotes/codings already live in the JSON data files.
data/deep/pdfs/
data/deep/txt/
data/raw/pdfs/
*.pdf

# Live link-check output is environment-specific (regenerate with check_links.py)
# (kept tracked by default; uncomment to ignore)
# data/link_check_report.json
